{
  "stem": "27150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this-- this was stopped because we didn't have the papers, the clearing papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because if you wanted to import, you had to export.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you were buying export papers to clear your imports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I went to the customs, and I got the 100 kilos out without anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You see, they were in aluminum, you see, sort of containers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- the factory started working, bottling, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the-- you see, that means we did whatever we could do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And was hard with transport to work, but somehow we managed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You see, Lola was in walking distance to her office, and-- but I always took a tram and a bus.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And somehow--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--well, it-- it was a very, very short story, you see, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean ?] seven day-- on the seventh day, you see, the-- the [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ranya ?] was yelling of victories at so and so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the seventh day there was a-- a advice that all able men should leave Warsaw and go east, you see.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- and so, we were sitting, so what-- how-- how-- how are we going east?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why should we walk?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Henry had a Buick, the company car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we said instead of going on the seventh, I don't know, sixth or the seventh at night, we will start in the morning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have a car, and we have plenty of petrol.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, In the meantime an officer came with a requisition card and took away the car.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we left back in Warsaw all during the invasion of Warsaw, you see, it wasn't a pleasant time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We listened to the radio.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three days later America declared-- England declared war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The French declared war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started to play French marches and English marches.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
